planation%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20senior%20party%20leader%20Supriya%20Sule%20called%20it%20'suspicious%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20a%20throwback%20to%20the%20multiple%20objections%20of%20the%20Opposition%20regarding%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines.%20The%20Returning%20Officer%20for%20the%20constituency%2C%20Kavita%20Dwivedi%2C%20has%20said%20only%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisplay%20was%20temporarily%20closed%26quot%3B.%20No%20reason%20was%20cited%20for%20this%20temporary%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCCTV%20system%20in%20warehouse%20where%20EVMs%20are%20kept%20in%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20Constituency%20fully%20operational.%20All%20data%20secure%2C%20only%20display%20temporarily%20closed-%20Explanation%20by%20Election%20Returning%20Officer%20Kavita%20Dwivedi%2C'%20read%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20by%20the%20District%20Information%20Office%2C%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bexplanation%26quot%3B%20came%20after%20a%20strong%20post%20from%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20the%20sitting%20MP%20who%20is%20defending%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20suspicious%20that%20the%20CCTV%20is%20switched%20off%20where%20a%20very%20important%20thing%20like%20EVM%20is%20kept.%20Also%2C%20this%20is%20a%20big%20laxity%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20rough%20translation%20of%20a%20Hindi%20post%20by%20Ms%20Sule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20election%20representatives%20contacted%20the%20concerned%20authorities%20and%20administration%2C%20no%20satisfactory%20answers%20were%20received.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20technician%20is%20also%20not%20available%20at%20the%20said%20place.%20Also%20our%20representatives%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20inspect%20the%20EVM%20status.%20This%20is%20very%20serious%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20further%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Election%20Commission%20should%20immediately%20take%20notice%20of%20this%20and%20announce%20the%20reasons%20why%20the%20CCTV%20was%20closed.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20appropriate%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20post%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaramati%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20Pawar%20versus%20Pawar%20fights%20in%20the%20state%20that%20took%20place%20today.%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20NCP%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20is%20up%20against%20her%20sister-in-law%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20her%20cousin%20and%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20election%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20has%20called%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20candidate%20%26quot%3Bdirty%20politics%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20last%20year%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20had%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP-Eknath%20Shinde%20alliance%20in%20a%20very%20public%20split%20that%20came%20as%20a%20huge%20loss%20of%20face%20for%20his%2083-year-old%20uncle.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%2012%20of%20the%20party's%2053%20MLAs%20have%20been%20supporting%20NCP%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%2041%20MLAs%20are%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20The%20MPs%20are%20split%20down%20the%20middle%2C%20with%20two%20MPs%20on%20each%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715611080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fs60agem_supriya-sule_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupriya-sule-alleges-cctv-in-evm-strongroom-switched-off-poll-officer-responds-5655211%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20the%20strongroom%20where%20Electronic%20Voting%20machines%20were%20stored%20for%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20Constituency%2C%20was%20switched%20off%20for%2045%20minutes%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20has%20alleged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupriya-sule-alleges-cctv-in-evm-strongroo