%20there.%20Instead%2C%20the%20officer%20can%20be%20found%20promenading%20through%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20campus%20which%20teems%20with%20abundant%20flowering%20plants%20and%20fruit%20trees.%20The%20sight%20of%20a%20glorious%20green%20carpet%20thriving%20at%20a%20height%20of%20300%20ft%20above%20sea%20level%20is%20baffling.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F163949%2Fjakkur-bengaluru-lake-pollution-cleaning-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especies%20of%20flora%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20you%20think%20reside%20within%20this%2025-acre%20land%3F%20Take%20a%20guess.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20850%20species%20and%20counting%2C%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20Chaturvedi.%20In%20this%20forest-like%20ecosystem%20that%20he%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20few%20years%20cultivating%2C%20bamboo%20and%20cactus%20befriend%20each%20other%2C%20while%20crickets%2C%20butterflies%20and%20insects%20stop%20by%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20to%20the%20honeysuckle.%20The%20air%20is%20crisp%20and%20the%20walk%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20Chaturvedi%2C%20who%20pauses%20to%20put%20his%20experience%20into%20words%3B%20then%20proceeds%20to%20say%20that%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20justice.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20most%20taken%20aback%20by%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20optimistic%20view%20are%20the%20naysayers%20who%20were%20convinced%20that%20this%20particular%20posting%20in%20the%20highlands%20of%20Uttarakhand%20would%20be%20a%20test%20of%20the%20IFS%20officer%E2%80%99s%20patience.%20Their%20discouragement%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20of%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20predecessors%20had%20detested%20being%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20god-forsaken%20area%2C%20made%20the%20officer%20sceptical.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302635%2Fladakh-ministry-of-education-score-new-heights-role-of-dedicated-teachers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20harsh%20terrain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20remoteness%20of%20the%20place%2C%20did%20nothing%20to%20ease%20his%20woes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20since%20he%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20conservator%20of%20forest%20research%20(Chaturvedi%20was%20promoted%20to%20head%20of%20the%20wing%20in%202020)%2C%20this%20terrain%20evolved%20into%20a%20blessing.%20As%20Chaturvedi%20and%20his%20team%20discovered%2C%20not%20only%20was%20it%20a%20favourable%20home%20for%20Nainital%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98miracle%20plant%E2%80%99%20Patwa%2C%20but%20also%20a%20host%20of%20other%20plant%20species%20that%20are%20in%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20red%20list%20and%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%98threatened%E2%80%99%20by%20Uttarakhand%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20has%20been%20working%20closely%20to%20conserve%20plant%20habitats%20and%20protect%20them%20from%20illegal%20trade.%20They%20are%20also%20innovating%20ways%20to%20grow%20them%20in%20their%20natural%20habitats%20and%20in%20their%20research%20centres%20as%20well.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20scale%20these%20plant%20populations%20at%20their%20original%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IFS%20Officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20has%20dedicated%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20to%20conserving%20endemic%20plant%20species%20in%20Nainital%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-300x157.jpg%20300w%2