%20there%20was%20on%20the%20ground.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20she%20was%20shocked%20and%20believed%20it%20could%20have%20been%20an%20explosion.%20Photos%20taken%20at%20the%20site%20revealed%20ice%20on%20the%20roof%20adjacent%20to%20a%20hole%2C%20with%20the%20shed's%20top%20punctured%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ice%20had%20fallen%20from%20a%20plane%2C%20which%20was%20the%20only%20logical%20explanation%20offered%20by%20the%20law%20enforcement%20personnel.%20%26quot%3BHe%20just%20said%20that%20we%20are%20below%20a%20flight%20path%20and%20it%20could%20have%20been%20ice%20from%20an%20airplane%2C%20which%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20could%20even%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Lewis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20said%20that%20she%20took%20the%20pet%20to%20the%20veterinarian%2C%20however%20it%20could%20not%20be%20saved%20and%20was%20euthanised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20also%20made%20requests%20for%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20event%20from%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20International%20Airport%20and%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Lewis%20stated%20that%20the%20FAA%20informed%20her%20that%20they%20are%20investigating%20the%20possible%20plane%20from%20which%20the%20ice%20fell.%20Notably%2C%20her%20house%20is%20on%20the%20airport's%20flight%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20every%20time%20I%20hear%20a%20plane%20go%20by%2C%20I'm%20thinking%20like%2C%20it's%20made%20me%20a%20little%20bit%20nervous%20about%20it%20happening%20again.%20We're%20just%20very%20unlucky%20apparently%20to%20have%20it%20hit%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715595600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F7dr8vpt_plane_625x300_13_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fice-chunk-falls-from-plane-kills-pet-goat-in-us-5653241%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20at%20least%20a%20b